title: Spacious Penthouse With Unmatched Views, Call Now!
posting_body: ['Welcome to Miro', 'Miro reflects the dynamic, multi-faceted character of contemporary life.', 'Start your day with a boost of energy at the fitness center, hone in on work from the comfortable co-working lounges, and wrap up the evening soaking up tranquility from the rooftop sky deck.', 'Come home to the perfect blend of easy relaxation, bold design, and quality finishes.', 'Live beyond your expectations.', 'Amenities Include:', 'Stainless Kitchen Appliance Suite', 'Swimming Pool', 'Paw Spa', 'Sundeck and Lounge Area', 'Bark Park', 'Contemporary European Cabinetry', 'Recycling', 'Private Game Lounge', 'Floor-to-Ceiling Windows', 'Dog Park', 'Conference Room', '24/7 Resident Ambassador Services', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!']
